flavor_text_entries.red:
Incredibly slow
and dopey. It
takes 5 seconds for it to feel
pain when under
attack.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
Incredibly slow
and dopey. It
takes 5 seconds for it to feel
pain when under
attack.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
Incredibly slow
and sluggish. It
is quite content to loll about
without worrying
about the time.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
It lazes vacantly
near water. If
something bites its tail, it won't
even notice for a
whole day.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
A sweet sap leaks
from its tail's
tip. Although not nutritious, the
tail is pleasant
to chew on.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
It is always so
absent-minded that
it won't react, even if its
flavorful tail is
bitten.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
SLOWPOKE uses its tail to catch prey by
dipping it in water at the side of a
river. However, this POKéMON often forgets
what it’s doing and often spends entire
days just loafing at water’s edge.

flavor_text_entries.alpha-sapphire:

at the side of a river. However, this Pokémon often forgets
what it’s doing and often spends entire days just loafing
at water’s edge.
flavor_text_entries.sun:
Its long tail often breaks off. It doesn’t really
feel any pain, though, and the tail grows back,
so Slowpoke isn’t particularly bothered.
flavor_text_entries.moon:
Alolan home cooking involves drying Slowpoke
tails and then simmering them into a salty stew.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-sun:
There are some places where Slowpoke is
worshiped because of a long-standing belief
that whenever Slowpoke yawns, it rains.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-moon:
Although their tails, which fall off naturally, can
easily be found lying around, they’re a precious
ingredient for cooking.
flavor_text_entries.lets-go-pikachu:
Incredibly slow and sluggish. It is quite content
to loll about without worrying about the time.
flavor_text_entries.lets-go-eevee:
Incredibly slow and sluggish. It is quite content
to loll about without worrying about the time.
flavor_text_entries.sword:
Slow-witted and oblivious, this Pokémon won’t
feel any pain if its tail gets eaten. It won’t notice
when its tail grows back, either.
flavor_text_entries.shield:
When this Pokémon’s tail is soaked in water,
sweetness seeps from it. Slowpoke uses this trait
to lure in and fish up other Pokémon.
